{
  "stem": "182.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 172.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were carrying these heavy suitcases, or some people had wicker baskets full with stuff.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the policemen with the-- with the whip, they were just beating them and-- and driving them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had nothing, so I helped a little.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And finally, we came to the train station, and everybody was loaded in train cars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Here, the most terrible experience was again, because you were with the-- I was-- you can cling to your mother or father, so you feel-- you don't feel so bad.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no facility to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a pot, and everybody had to go on that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, this is, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is such a dehumanizing [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] something, when there is 4-- there are 40 people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You are on top of each other, and you have to use this pot, and it sloshes, and it-- it's terrible.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, we had a little food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father didn't want to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then we had to tell that my mother, Daddy, this is getting spoiled already, so eat it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it remained-- when we came back and we were [INAUDIBLE], remained the joke that we have to tell daddy that this is getting spoiled, he should eat.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my father was very worried because we already knew that how these Germans are and what's happening in Poland, when we heard that they were killing the mothers with their babies in their arms, and-- and throwing people alive into the river to drown, tied them together and they drowned and atro-- atroc-- atrocities like that.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't expect anything good from this to come out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But still, there was a ray of hope that they will take us and we will work.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
